calculator

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • calculator.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    A model for entry.

    An entry could be any numbers, operators or strings, each has a constructor
    and a getter method. There is also a method which can get the type of this
    entry.

    Author:
    Bruce
